<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Savory Bistro - Menu & Reviews</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Reset & Styling */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #fcfbfa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517248135467-4c7edcad34c4?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80') no-repeat center center/cover;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ff9f1c;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
            color: #2ec4b6;
        }

        h2::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 60px;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: #ff9f1c;
            margin: 10px auto 0;
        }

        /* --- MENU SECTION --- */
        .menu-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .menu-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .menu-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .menu-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .menu-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .menu-title-price {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .menu-title-price h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #111;
        }

        .price {
            color: #ff9f1c;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .menu-info p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* --- MULTIMEDIA CONTROLS SECTION --- */
        .media-section {
            background-color: #f1f0ea;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .media-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 30px;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .video-container, .audio-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        video {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            outline: none;
            background-color: #000;
        }

        audio {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 15px;
            outline: none;
        }

        /* Styling native multimedia controls using CSS properties */
        video::-webkit-media-controls-panel,
        audio::-webkit-media-controls-panel {
            background-color: #2ec4b6;
        }

        video::-webkit-media-controls-play-button,
        audio::-webkit-media-controls-play-button {
            background-color: #ff9f1c;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        video::-webkit-media-controls-current-time-display,
        audio::-webkit-media-controls-current-time-display {
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* --- REVIEWS SECTION --- */
        .reviews-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .review-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 5px solid #ff9f1c;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
        }

        .stars {
            color: #ff9f1c;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .review-text {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .reviewer-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #111;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-align: right;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #111;
            color: #aaa;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>The Savory Bistro</h1>
        <p>Fresh ingredients, timeless recipes, unforgettable moments</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">

        <section>
            <h2>Our Signature Menu</h2>
            <div class="menu-grid">
                
                <div class="menu-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565299624946-b28f40a0ae38?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Margherita Pizza" class="menu-img">
                    <div class="menu-info">
                        <div class="menu-title-price">
                            <h3>Artisan Margherita</h3>
                            <span class="price">$14.99</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Fresh mozzarella, san marzano tomatoes, torn basil, and a drizzle of extra virgin olive oil on a charred crust.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="menu-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546069901-ba9599a7e63c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Salmon Salad" class="menu-img">
                    <div class="menu-info">
                        <div class="menu-title-price">
                            <h3>Pan-Seared Salmon Bowl</h3>
                            <span class="price">$21.50</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Atlantic salmon served over a bed of organic quinoa, roasted sweet potatoes, avocado slices, and citrus dressing.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="menu-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551024601-bec78aea704b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Chocolate Lava Cake" class="menu-img">
                    <div class="menu-info">
                        <div class="menu-title-price">
                            <h3>Molten Lava Cake</h3>
                            <span class="price">$8.25</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Rich Belgian chocolate cake with a delightfully liquid center, served alongside premium Madagascar vanilla bean gelato.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="media-section">
            <h2>Experience The Vibe</h2>
            <p>Take a virtual tour inside our kitchen and listen to our curated dinner playlist.</p>
            
            <div class="media-wrapper">
                <div class="video-container">
                    <h4 style="margin-bottom:10px;">Behind the Scenes</h4>
                    <video controls poster="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556910103-1c02745aae4d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80">
                        <source src="https://www.w3schools.com/html/mov_bbb.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        Your browser does not support the video tag.
                    </video>
                </div>

                <div class="audio-container">
                    <h4 style="margin-bottom:10px;">Bistro Ambient Jazz</h4>
                    <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:#666; margin-bottom:10px;">The exact tunes playing at our tables tonight.</p>
                    <audio controls>
                        <source src="https://www.w3schools.com/html/horse.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
                        Your browser does not support the audio element.
                    </audio>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Guest Reviews</h2>
            <div class="reviews-container">
                
                <div class="review-card">
                    <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                    <p class="review-text">"The Margherita pizza tasted just like the ones I had in Naples. Fantastic service and gorgeous rustic atmosphere!"</p>
                    <div class="reviewer-name">— Sophia L.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="review-card">
                    <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                    <p class="review-text">"That molten lava cake is out of this world. I've recommended this place to all my friends already."</p>
                    <div class="reviewer-name">— Marcus T.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="review-card">
                    <div class="stars">★★★★☆</div>
                    <p class="review-text">"Healthy and delicious options. The salmon was cooked to perfect crispiness. Will definitely dine here again."</p>
                    <div class="reviewer-name">— Clara Henderson</div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 The Savory Bistro. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
